450
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:11,180
It's been so many years.

451
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:14,195
Even so, the writing is as beautiful as ever.

452
00:41:14,195 --> 00:41:16,504

453
00:41:31,700 --> 00:41:34,942
Second Senior, I have a question.

454
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:39,760
I'm now considered an official disciple, right?

455
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,860
Of course. The ceremony is over.

456
00:41:41,860 --> 00:41:44,220
Why am I getting myself a master?

457
00:41:44,220 --> 00:41:47,120
- To learn martial arts. 
 - If so, where's my master?

458
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:50,140
Even Luoxia has moved to Senior Liu Yue's residence to learn martial arts from him.

459
00:41:50,140 --> 00:41:55,080
But my master? He's busy with everything except teaching me martial arts.

460
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:58,580
Although you have a master in order to learn martial arts,

461
00:41:58,580 --> 00:42:03,240
Master didn't say that he was going to teach you, right?

462
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:06,040
Disciples have to learn the skills by themselves.

463
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:08,440
If so, what's the use of having a master?

464
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:12,982
Of course it's for you to say his name and terrify your foes

465
00:42:12,982 --> 00:42:14,980
